# PyMOL script to highlight allosteric sites in 1G3L
fetch 1G3L
hide everything
show cartoon, chain C
color spectrum, chain C
# Highlight allosteric residues
select resi 251 and chain C
show surface, resi 251 and chain C
color green, resi 251 and chain C
set transparency, 0.19999999999999996, resi 251 and chain C
